text: Albi Prifti (born 5 August 1993 in Fier) is an Albanian retired footballer who played for Apolonia Fier in the Albanian Superliga.Soccerway profile His older brother Andi also plays for Apolonia Fier. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Sportspeople from Fier Category:Association football midfielders Category:Albanian footballers Category:KF Apolonia Fier players Category:Albanian Superliga players Category:Albanian First Division players
